* HELO transaction -- 43x80 layout for mod 4 / alt-screen terminals.
* Mirrors the named slots from helo1.map (INFOLINE, GREETING, FOOTER) so
* the same SCR. stem feeds either map; adds INFO1-3 and ACT1-3 panels
* that only fit on a 43-row screen.
MAP HELO1L SIZE 43x80
  FIELD INFOLINE AT 0,0   LEN 78 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=TURQUOISE
  FIELD GREETING AT 5,5   LEN 20 PROT BRIGHT COLOR=WHITE

  * --- panels that only fit on a mod-4 screen ---
  FIELD AT 13,2  LEN 25 PROT DIM    COLOR=TURQUOISE  "System information:"
  FIELD INFO1    AT 15,4  LEN 70 PROT COLOR=WHITE
  FIELD INFO2    AT 16,4  LEN 70 PROT COLOR=WHITE
  FIELD INFO3    AT 17,4  LEN 70 PROT COLOR=WHITE

  FIELD AT 22,2  LEN 25 PROT DIM    COLOR=TURQUOISE  "Recent activity:"
  FIELD ACT1     AT 24,4  LEN 70 PROT COLOR=WHITE
  FIELD ACT2     AT 25,4  LEN 70 PROT COLOR=WHITE
  FIELD ACT3     AT 26,4  LEN 70 PROT COLOR=WHITE

  FIELD FOOTER   AT 41,2  LEN 60 PROT DIM    COLOR=BLUE
ENDMAP
